author: @avirupdutta4306
text: Improve your problem solving skills, whatever you are studying think about how you can utilise that to resolve an production issue. Whenever you are studying something, have the concept clear because in Product based company, interview are not like what is this and that, question will be like such that you might not come across yet but you will be knowing the solution and you just have to implement or explain the solution.
